data.description: WOW!  What a beauty! Lovely STARFISH model with LAKEFRONT views.Impeccable 2021 home, 3 bedroom, 2 bath with 2 car garage.  Owners have added a serene screened enclosure overlooking the lake view.Special information:  ASSUMABLE MORTGAGE of  5.1% Interest rate available to Buyers with Letter of Intent. (Current mortgage balance is approximately $409k.)Beautifully upgraded kitchen with Quartz countertops, pull out shelving and GE Upgraded package stainless appliances....also gas cooking!! Your center island is equipped with a deep sink.All windows are impact giving you quiet days and nights. The bedrooms are carpeted with upgraded luxury carpeting.  You have a tankless water heater system and piped natural gas.Dont wait on this one.  Make your appointment today!
